snippet.title: Captain Blast'Em!
snippet.description:
Welcome to the Captain Blastem Youtube Channel! We do videos on the weekdays and streams on the weekend; if you enjoy funny gaming videos featuring Horror Games like Resident Evil on the weekends, Crafting Games Like Minecraft and Subnautica, and Co-Op Multiplayer like It Takes Two, Town of Salem, and Among us, then this is the growing youtube channel for you! I do my best to focus on family-friendly commentary with lots of Hilarious moments, epic fails, a dash of memes, some slight innuendo; and a good amount of rage quitting.

Twitch: https://twitch.tv/cappyb_

Twitter: https://twitter.com/valeyard
